WEBVTT

00:00.487 --> 00:02.339
First the tour, now the group.

00:02.709 --> 00:05.713
Zayn Malik has officially left One Direction.

00:06.007 --> 00:08.437
The British pop sensation has confirmed the news Wednesday,...

00:08.671 --> 00:11.114
...a week after Zayn left the group's world tour...

00:11.187 --> 00:13.585
...citing stress and flew back to the UK.

00:13.970 --> 00:16.915
In a statement, he says he wants to be a normal 22-year-old...

00:17.087 --> 00:18.781
...who can relax out of the spotlight.

